      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Potential for analyst-induced errors in model setup, boundary condition specification, and post-processing must be evaluated through independent review or replicate analyses.",
      "rationale": "No independent verification of model setup or boundary condition inputs was conducted. Analyst self-review was performed but no formal use-error assessment protocol was applied. Factor left not-assessed."
