      "acceptanceCriteria": "The choice of turbulence model, hemolysis damage model, and constitutive equations must be justified relative to the flow physics and validated against independent data.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence closure and the Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law model were selected based on prior literature but no formal model-form uncertainty quantification was performed for this COU. Factor not assessed."
