    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The assessment team concluded that the seven assessed credibility factors collectively provide sufficient evidence to accept the CFD hemolysis model for the CPB COU. Assessed factors all meet or exceed required levels. The four not-assessed factors (numerical solver error, use error, model form, test samples) were noted but not formally evaluated. The team determined that the overall body of validation evidence supports the acceptance decision for regulatory submission purposes.",
